<br>
“Yes?”<br>
<br>
“D’you think mother should have told him?”<br>
<br>
“About you?”  Cassandra shook her head.  “I don’t know enough to make a judgement.  No one can, except your mother and father, my dear.”<br>
<br>
Delaine nodded again.  “I guess I’ll have to think about it.”<br>
<br>
Cassandra nodded in agreement and opened the door.<br>
