<br>
“That will be fine.”<br>
<br>
The half-elf beamed a wide smile at him.<br>
<br>
“Oh, thank you, sir.”<br>
<br>
And she ran off.<br>
<br>
Dalain stared after her in her wake, bemusedly.  What was that all about?  And… who did she remind him off?  That was quite a glorious smile.  With a shrug, he waved at the other warriors sparring in the arena and walked to North Freeport, sprinting from the guards when they caught sight of him until he reached the sanctity of the Paladin controlled North boundary.<br>
