<br>
“I’m sorry.  You must think me awfully ill mannered.  I… I apologize for swearing in front of you.  I.. I mean..”<br>
<br>
Her voice trailed off into silence and she looked down at her hands before peeking up at him.<br>
<br>
Her mannerism struck a deep chord within him, and an image flashed into his mind.  But she was speaking again, and he forced his mind to the here and now.<br>
<br>
“Well, sir.  I… umm… I…”<br>
<br>
